				<wikidot:authorName>ShadowSpirit90</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6753095</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I enjoyed this, it going from a series of events as the scip to just being the crystal ball, but I do have one problem.<br /> In the footnote where you listed the Stevens family, you listed the father as Kyle, but in the interview log, the interviewee is James. So, either they interviewed a heretofore unmentioned member of the Stevens family, which you may want to add to the footnote, or you named the father incorrectly in the footnote.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
