					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Spooky ghost story ~</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers/Ramblings</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Boo!</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>So there's a thread of fridge logic regarding the crystal ball I'd like to touch on. The ball was previously used by a psychic that did séances for locals, seeing how the ball is only capable of making illusions, it can be assumed that the psychic used the ball to trick towns people into thinking they're talking to dead relatives. Ramblings over.</p> </div> </div> </div> <br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> Critters: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4916887&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589925117" alt="MalyceGraves" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4916887)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/malycegraves" >MalyceGraves</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3352053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589925117" alt="Cerastes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3352053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cerastes" >Cerastes</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drhawkwind" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=993076&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589925117" alt="DrHawkwind" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=993076)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drhawkwind" >DrHawkwind</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-dune" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6151547&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1589925117" alt="Doctor Dune" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6151547)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-dune" >Doctor Dune</a></span>, anyone I forgot can just give me a poke.
